In [6]:
def conv_time(time):
    hr = int(time.split(":")[0])
    minute = time.split(":")[1]
    
    return float(round(hr + int(minute)/60, 3))
In [7]:

Take a look at OD¶

In [13]:
plot_list = []
for n, group in enumerate(df['Sample'].unique()):
    sub_df = df.loc[df['Sample'] == group]
    sub_df = sub_df.sort_values(['Time', 'well'])
    
    p = bokeh.plotting.figure(height = 300,
                              width = 600,
                              x_range = (0, 20),
                              title = group,
                              x_axis_label = 'Time (Hours)',
                              y_axis_label = 'OD700', 
                              y_range = (0, 1.2))

    for i, inducer in enumerate(sub_df.Inducer.unique()):
        color = color_list[i]
        inducer_df = sub_df.loc[sub_df.Inducer == inducer]

        for well in inducer_df['well'].unique():
            
            curve = inducer_df.loc[inducer_df['well'] == well]
            curve  = curve.sort_values('Time')
            p.line(curve.Time, curve.OD700, color = color, width = 1.5)
            
    if n == 4:
        r1 = p.circle(0, 0, color = color_list[0], width = 0)
        r2 = p.circle(0, 0, color = color_list[1], width = 0)
        r3 = p.circle(0, 0, color = color_list[2], width = 0)
        r4 = p.circle(0, 0, color = color_list[3], width = 0)
        
        legend = Legend(items=[
                    ("None"   , [r1]),
                    ("Tetrathionate" , [r2]),
                    ("IPTG or ATC" , [r3]),
                    ("Both Inducers", [r4])
                ])

        p.add_layout(legend, 'right')
        
    p.title.text_font_size = '18pt'
    p.yaxis.axis_label_text_font_size = '15pt'
    p.xaxis.axis_label_text_font_size = '15pt'

    p.xaxis.axis_label_text_font_style = 'normal'
    p.yaxis.axis_label_text_font_style = 'normal'

    p.xaxis.major_label_text_font_size = '10pt'
    p.yaxis.major_label_text_font_size = '10pt'

    plot_list.append(p)
In [14]:

plot_list = []

for i, inducer in enumerate(df.Inducer.unique()):
    print(inducer)
    sub_df = df.loc[df['Inducer'] == inducer]
    sub_df = sub_df.sort_values(['Time', 'well'])
    
    p = bokeh.plotting.figure(height = 2100,
                              width = 2900,
                              x_range = (0, 22),
#                               y_range = (0, 6000),
                              title = inducer,
                              x_axis_label = 'Time (hr)',
                              y_axis_label = 'Fluor/ OD₇₀₀ (10⁴)')

    for n, group in enumerate(['LM42']):
        color = color_list2[n]
        sample_df = sub_df.loc[sub_df.Sample == group]

        for well in sample_df['well'].unique():
            curve = sample_df.loc[sample_df['well'] == well]
            curve  = curve.sort_values('Time')
            p.line(curve.Time, curve.GFP / curve.OD700 / 10e3, color = color_list2[3], width = 11, legend_label = 'GFP')
            p.line(curve.Time, curve.mScarlet / curve.OD700 / 10e3, color = color_list2[5], width = 11, legend_label = 'mScarlet')
        
    if i == 0:
        p.legend.glyph_width = 150
        p.legend.glyph_height = 150
        p.legend.label_text_font_size = "150pt"       
    else:
        p.legend.visible = False

    p.xaxis.axis_label_text_font_style = 'normal'
    p.yaxis.axis_label_text_font_style = 'normal'
    
    p.xaxis.major_tick_line_width = 10
    p.yaxis.major_tick_line_width = 10
    
    p.xaxis.minor_tick_line_width = 10
    p.yaxis.minor_tick_line_width = 10
    
    p.axis.minor_tick_out = 20
    p.axis.minor_tick_out = 20
    
    p.axis.major_tick_out = 40
    p.axis.major_tick_out = 40
    p.yaxis.axis_label_standoff = 50
    p.xaxis.axis_label_standoff = 50
    
    p.xaxis.axis_line_width = 8
    p.yaxis.axis_line_width = 8

    p.yaxis.major_label_standoff = 30
    p.xaxis.major_label_standoff = 30
    
    p.ygrid.grid_line_width = 10
    p.xgrid.grid_line_width = 10
    
    p.title.text_font_size = '180pt'
   
    p.xaxis.major_label_text_font_size = "160pt"
    p.yaxis.major_label_text_font_size = "160pt"

    p.xaxis.axis_label_text_font_size = "130pt"
    p.yaxis.axis_label_text_font_size = "130pt"


    plot_list.append(p)
